    <note>Zhao(1) Xiao [20955] His ancestors moved from Shaoxing to Wukang and then to Ruian. This origin is the same as that of Zhao(1) Bian's [375] lineage and Xiao has the same generational name as Bian's grandsons, which makes it almost certain that the families of Bian and Xiao derive from the same root lineage. Xiao's funerary inscription contains information on property division. Zhou Xingji, WJ, 7.7b-9b. CBD, 4, 3361-2.</note>
